Use these robot tests for Component Integration tests as defined in the wiki:

https://wiki.sophos.net/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=317105394

In order to run these tests in tap do:
 1) activate the tap environment:
    source tap/bin/activate
 2) tap run template_plugin.integration --debug-loop

In order to run them in vagrant box:
    vagrant up
    vagrant ssh
    sudo mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs
    sudo mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs/template_plugin/
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-template/output/SDDS-COMPONENT /opt/test/inputs/template_plugin_sdds
    sudo  rm /opt/test/inputs/test_scripts
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-template/TA  /opt/test/inputs/test_scripts
    sudo cp -r /vagrant/everest-base/output/SDDS-COMPONENT /opt/test/inputs/base_sdds
    sudo apt-get -y install python3.7 python3-pip
    sudo -H python3 -m pip install pyzmq protobuf pytest-html robotframework
    cd /vagrant/sspl-plugin-template/TA
    sudo python3 -m robot RobotTests/




